{"type":null,"faqId":38488,"title":"多屏互动","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p4{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>使用多屏互动，可以将手机上的图片、视频或游戏推送到电视机或其他屏幕上呈现，和家人好友一起分享欢乐时光。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>电视机不支持多屏互动？没关系，只要电视机支持 HDMI，您就可以选购 Android TV Box（媒体伴侣）或其他类似的无线传输设备来实现此功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>打开通知面板，在“开关”页签下，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125366\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，然后选择接收端设备，开启多屏互动功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125367\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>关于手机与 Android TV Box 连接的方法和使用指导，请参考 Android TV Box 产品的相关资料。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":1,"unUseful":4,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3768","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441442758000,"seriesProductName":"GRA-CL00,GRA-CL10,GRA-TL00,GRA-UL00,GRA-UL10","visitedTimes":190,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"多屏互动","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}